=Generate onboarding materials for a new client.

Company: {{ $json.original_input.company_name }}
Contact: {{ $json.original_input.primary_contact }} ({{ $json.original_input.contact_title }})
ARR: ${{ $json.original_input.arr }}
Sales Team: {{ $json.original_input.sales_team_size }}
CRM: {{ $json.original_input.crm }}
Scope: {{ $json.original_input.scope_tier }}
Duration: {{ $json.original_input.duration }}
Start: {{ $json.original_input.start_date }}
Challenges: {{ $json.original_input.challenges }}

Generate: 1) Welcome email (professional, warm, lists what you need from them), 2) Onboarding checklist (CRM access, data exports, stakeholder intros, etc.), 3) First 30 days task list (Discovery/Assessment/Recommendations/Execution phases with specific tasks, owners, and estimates), 4) Kickoff meeting agenda (90 min). Format as markdown sections.
